# UI/UX Standards

## Design language (v20+)
- Light theme: `#f2f3f4` bg, white cards, `#0c831f` primary green
- Sticky topbar: patient + hospital + live pill
- Bottom nav: Home | Bills | + | Share | Care
- Quick action chips on Home (horizontal scroll)
- Order-style bill history (newest first)

## Mobile-first checklist
- Touch targets ≥ 44px
- Bottom nav + safe-area insets (`env(safe-area-inset-bottom)`)
- Test 320px–414px widths
- One-thumb reach for primary actions (+ add bill)

## Product questions (ask before building)
- Can this screen be simpler?
- Can one tap be removed?
- Would Blinkit/Apple build it this way?
- Can loading feel smoother (skeleton > spinner > blank)?

## Loading & states
- Above-fold Home content: **visible immediately** (no `.reveal` delay on critical data)
- Skeleton shimmer for `grandTotal`, `homePaid`, `careBanner` when loading
- Splash tied to `loadData()` completion, not fixed timeout
- Empty states: friendly copy + CTA ("tap + to add")

## Tone
- WhatsApp/share: respectful Telugu, family-safe
- Settlement UI: "Fair adjustment · సమన్యయం" — never accusatory
- Badges: "Balance" / "Credit" not "MUST PAY"

## Do not regress
- Tab navigation (v17+)
- Warm WhatsApp message (v21)
- "Powered by Tevs" footer unless user removes
